<td>part (compare "dole", "deal")</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td rowspan="2"><b>High German b = Low German w (v sound), f</b></td>
<td>Leben</td>
<td>Lewen, Läwen</td>
<td>Läwe(n)</td>
<td>leven</td>
<td>life</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Korb</td>
<td>Korf</td>
<td>Korf</td>
