<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Plautdietsch_language&action=edit&section=20.php.html" title="Edit section: Phonetics">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Phonetics">Phonetics</span></h2>
<p>Mennonite Low German has many sounds, including a few not found in other varieties of Low German.</p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Plautdietsch_language&action=edit&section=21.php.html" title="Edit section: Consonants">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Consonants">Consonants</span></h3>
